# **Client Base & Positioning TAB — COMPLETE BUILD SPECIFICATION**

## **DOCUMENT OVERVIEW**

This specification defines the complete build for the **Growth & Pipeline** tab within the Agency Snapshot feature. This tab captures current-state revenue model, client profile, retention health, and acquisition efficiency to characterize the agency's business model and strategic implications.

**Visual Reference:** Match layout and styling of Financial tab exactly.

