## **CALCULATED METRICS (7 Real-Time Calculations)**

These calculate immediately as users enter data (client-side JavaScript):

### **Calculation 1: Average Client Value (ACV)**

**Field Name:** `calculated_acv`  
 **Formula:**

javascript  
const monthly\_agi \= getFromFinancialTab('monthly\_agi');  
const client\_count \= active\_client\_count;

if (monthly\_agi && client\_count \> 0\) {  
  calculated\_acv \= monthly\_agi / client\_count;  
} else {  
  calculated\_acv \= null;  
}

**Display Format:** $X,XXX per month per client  
 **Conditional Display:** Only show if both AGI (from Financial tab) and client count are provided  
 **Label:** "Average Client Value (ACV)"

---

### **Calculation 2: MRR (Dollars)**

**Field Name:** `calculated_mrr_dollars`  
 **Formula:**

javascript  
const monthly\_agi \= getFromFinancialTab('monthly\_agi');  
const mrr\_pct \= revenue\_mix\_mrr\_percentage;

if (monthly\_agi && mrr\_pct \!== null) {  
  calculated\_mrr\_dollars \= monthly\_agi \* (mrr\_pct / 100);  
} else {  
  calculated\_mrr\_dollars \= null;  
}

**Display Format:** $XXX,XXX  
 **Label:** "Monthly Recurring Revenue"

---

### **Calculation 3: Project Revenue (Dollars)**

**Field Name:** `calculated_project_dollars`  
 **Formula:**

javascript  
const monthly\_agi \= getFromFinancialTab('monthly\_agi');  
const project\_pct \= 100 \- revenue\_mix\_mrr\_percentage;

if (monthly\_agi && revenue\_mix\_mrr\_percentage \!== null) {  
  calculated\_project\_dollars \= monthly\_agi \* (project\_pct / 100);  
} else {  
  calculated\_project\_dollars \= null;  
}

**Display Format:** $XXX,XXX  
 **Label:** "Project Revenue"

---

### **Calculation 4: Annual Churn Rate**

**Field Name:** `calculated_annual_churn_pct`  
 **Formula:**

javascript  
if (monthly\_churn\_rate \!== null) {  
  calculated\_annual\_churn\_pct \= monthly\_churn\_rate \* 12;  
  // Note: This is rough approximation, actual compound \= different  
  // But sufficient for directional insight  
} else {  
  calculated\_annual\_churn\_pct \= null;  
}

**Display Format:** \~XX% annual turnover  
 **Label:** "Annual Churn Rate (Approximate)"

---

### **Calculation 5: Annual Churned Clients**

**Field Name:** `calculated_annual_churned_clients`  
 **Formula:**

javascript  
if (active\_client\_count && monthly\_churn\_rate \!== null) {  
  const annual\_churn\_pct \= monthly\_churn\_rate \* 12;  
  calculated\_annual\_churned\_clients \= Math.round(  
    active\_client\_count \* (annual\_churn\_pct / 100\)  
  );  
} else {  
  calculated\_annual\_churned\_clients \= null;  
}

**Display Format:** \~X clients per year  
 **Label:** "Churned Clients Annually"

---

### **Calculation 6: Implied Replacement Rate**

**Field Name:** `calculated_replacement_rate`  
 **Formula:**

javascript  
if (monthly\_churn\_rate \!== null) {  
  calculated\_replacement\_rate \= monthly\_churn\_rate;  
  // The replacement rate equals the churn rate  
  // This is the % growth needed monthly just to stay flat  
} else {  
  calculated\_replacement\_rate \= null;  
}

**Display Format:** Must grow X.X% monthly to maintain revenue  
 **Label:** "Implied Replacement Rate"  
 **Helper Text Below:** "This is the minimum monthly growth rate needed to offset churn and stay neutral (not counting upsells)"

---

### **Calculation 7: Concentration Risk Score**

**Field Name:** `calculated_concentration_risk`  
 **Formula:**

let riskScore \= 'LOW';  
let riskReason \= '';

const top5 \= concentration\_top5\_pct;  
const top10 \= concentration\_top10\_pct;  
const top20 \= concentration\_top20\_pct;

if (top5 \> 70 || top10 \> 85 || top20 \> 95\) {  
  riskScore \= 'HIGH';  
  riskReason \= 'Extremely concentrated client base';  
} else if (top5 \> 50 || top10 \> 70 || top20 \> 85\) {  
  riskScore \= 'MEDIUM';  
  riskReason \= 'Notable concentration in top clients';  
} else if (top5 \!== null || top10 \!== null || top20 \!== null) {  
  riskScore \= 'LOW';  
  riskReason \= 'Well-distributed client base';  
} else {  
  riskScore \= null;  
  riskReason \= '';  
}  
\`\`\`

\*\*Display Format:\*\*  
\`\`\`  
Concentration Risk: \[HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW\]  
(Top 5: X%, Top 10: Y%)  
\`\`\`

\*\*Color Coding:\*\*  
\- HIGH \= Red text  
\- MEDIUM \= Yellow/orange text  
\- LOW \= Green text

