\#\# \*\*BENCHMARKS FOR SYNTHESIS\*\*

\#\#\# \*\*Revenue Mix (MRR %):\*\*  
\- \*\*80%+\*\* → Very stable, recurring-heavy (subscription model)  
\- \*\*60-80%\*\* → Balanced, healthy mix  
\- \*\*40-60%\*\* → Project-heavy with some recurring  
\- \*\*\<40%\*\* → Primarily project/transactional

\#\#\# \*\*Monthly Churn Rate:\*\*  
\- \*\*\<1.5%\*\* → Excellent retention (85%+ annual retention)  
\- \*\*1.5-2.5%\*\* → Healthy (70-82% annual retention)  
\- \*\*2.5-4%\*\* → Moderate concern (52-70% annual retention)  
\- \*\*4%+\*\* → High concern (\<52% annual retention)

\#\#\# \*\*Concentration Risk Thresholds:\*\*

\*\*Top 5 Clients:\*\*  
\- \*\*\>70%\*\* \= HIGH RISK (extremely concentrated)  
\- \*\*50-70%\*\* \= MEDIUM RISK (notable concentration)  
\- \*\*\<50%\*\* \= LOW RISK (distributed)

\*\*Top 10 Clients:\*\*  
\- \*\*\>85%\*\* \= HIGH RISK  
\- \*\*70-85%\*\* \= MEDIUM RISK  
\- \*\*\<70%\*\* \= LOW RISK

\*\*Top 20 Clients:\*\*  
\- \*\*\>95%\*\* \= HIGH RISK  
\- \*\*85-95%\*\* \= MEDIUM RISK  
\- \*\*\<85%\*\* \= LOW RISK

\*\*Overall Risk Score Logic:\*\*  
\- If ANY threshold triggers HIGH → Overall \= HIGH  
\- If ANY threshold triggers MEDIUM (and no HIGH) → Overall \= MEDIUM  
\- If all thresholds are LOW → Overall \= LOW

\#\#\# \*\*Win Rate:\*\*  
\- \*\*50%+\*\* → Excellent (top quartile)  
\- \*\*40-50%\*\* → Strong (above average)  
\- \*\*30-40%\*\* → Industry standard  
\- \*\*20-30%\*\* → Below average  
\- \*\*\<20%\*\* → Concerning

